column5: I couldnt get out for opening day, but today I did. The conditions were perfect, a little rain, cloud cover and cool air, what more do you need for some walter success.
Sounds like you had fun   Vince Beauty eye dude
Nice work. Glad to see you can still catch some fish lol.
Nice one Vin !!! Glad you got out.
Way to go Vin. A really nice, clean, well coloured fish too! Thanks for showing.
Nice going Vince, we'll see if you can top that one Saturday.
Good stuff Vince - made for a tasty supper I bet

Thanks guys, considering the time of day regardless of conditions, I really had my doubts on catching one. And so be I did on my third cast, after that not a sniff anywhere along that waterbody. And I have tried , truelly I have, to get my three under the slot. And not another stinking sniff, and i cant complain at all . As my youngest would put it, booooooya baby!!!, what ever that means
Hush, Frankie... There's only one person that can top that on Saturday-moi (kidding)! Nice work, Vince!
